    <div class="main review-item" id="5434096">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5434096/" class="title-link">学习粤语的非常棒的教材</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5434096"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/23865995/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u23865995-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/23865995/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Dagger</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-05-19"
      class="main-meta">2012-05-19 20:48:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5434096_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  学习粤语的非常棒的教材，发音、语法都讲得很不错。中篇还有些发音的总结。比看电视和与广东人或香港人直接学习，来的快。学完之后，可以说简单的粤语，唱粤语歌没问题了。可以唱beyond的歌了。 感觉很不错。嘿嘿。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
