            <div id="review_5434096_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7568824">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7568824/" class="title-link">脱离实际</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7568824"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/53111668/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u53111668-28.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/53111668/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Limmok </span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-08-13"
      class="main-meta">2015-08-13 18:15:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7568824_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  标榜是香港话，但是书内语言不生活化，很多用语香港人根本不讲（我在香港工作）。还有很多老旧词，在新版依然没剔除（什么“镭射影碟”之类的）。在书的后半部分，书面语风格越来越重，总之，这本书与生活粤语，日常交际比较脱节。修订版依然如此。差评。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7568824_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7568824_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



